{"tid":1950760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報導，中國28日新增一例香港肺炎本土病例。","createTime":"2020-03-30T13:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T13:55:15.000Z","uid":8922,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b07946c47fd5f8f478ca1f3af5c038e10e34a5b7","tid":1950760,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"當你地仲討論緊項明生同港女<br />\n支共已經射緊個波俾香港<br />\n<br />\n另據報導，中國28日新增一例香港肺炎本土病例。據通報，這名來自河南的病例是&ldquo;無症狀感染者的密切接觸者&rdquo;。中國國家衛健委週日通報，28日共新增新冠肺炎確診45例，其中44例為境外輸入，唯一本土新增病例來自河南省。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>殘體慎入</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200329-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%99%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD-%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%96%E7%95%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E7%8C%9C%E6%B5%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%2F20200329-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%2582%25B9%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%2585%25B3%25E9%2597%25AD-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%258F%2591%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25AF%25B9%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25AE%259E%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2586%25B5%25E7%258C%259C%25E6%25B5%258B&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2SaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=9593c70e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20200329-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%AD%89%E5%9C%B0%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%99%AF%E7%82%B9%E5%86%8D%E5%BA%A6%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD-%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%A4%96%E7%95%8C%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%9E%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%E7%8C%9C%E6%B5%8B</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ES-ny8aUYAAHkYF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FES-ny8aUYAAHkYF.jpg&h=242bd72c&s={SIZE}\" />"